{"tid":789692,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有錢人同窮人自己煮野食既分別","createTime":"2018-08-22T12:11:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-22T12:39:01.000Z","uid":42188,"like":36,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e501dc5ed64bcf96cb9e306eb9ecefb399c1037f","tid":789692,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T12:11:57.000Z","msg":"有錢人自己煮野食係求健康<br />\n買既餸全部都係優質食材<br />\n多數都唔會買支那野<br />\n<br />\n而窮人自己煮野食係因為食唔起出面既野食<br />\n佢地會自慰話出面野食唔健康<br />\n呢樣係真<br />\n但佢地買返來既餸全部都係垃圾食材<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果講到為健康著想，就唔會買垃圾食材啦<br />\n說穿了，因為冇錢買優質食材<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我預咗會有好多負評<br />\n無計啦，連登咁多公屋仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e50177e7ac74428dead56f3654fa1d4b77278b2","tid":789692,"uid":202983,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T12:23:43.000Z","msg":"好奇一問 優質同劣質食材姐係 新鮮同唔新鮮 定有機同冇機果啲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bebf0a85c3662ec8aa4fabef8c3b321a1c59e75f","tid":789692,"uid":53498,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T12:24:30.000Z","msg":"五毛公屋系列"},{"pid":"cb20e52d227032172d20b4ab921ab2a9e8e4420a","tid":789692,"uid":35106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T12:24:59.000Z","msg":"根本愈窮就愈易肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2fefac208779b5857a3b544295e077cdc15bbfd","tid":789692,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3e50177e7ac74428dead56f3654fa1d4b77278b2","tid":789692,"uid":202983,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T12:23:43.000Z","msg":"好奇一問 優質同劣質食材姐係 新鮮同唔新鮮 定有機同冇機果啲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T12:35:03.000Z","msg":"淨係唔食支那野 已經高一班"},{"pid":"2a011800dfde9075c658db909bb92b4a36a2cf6c","tid":789692,"uid":190818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T12:39:01.000Z","msg":"自己煮買啲料仲貴過出街食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但煮下飯仔係幾正"}]}